015-06-23|publisher=新浪娱乐|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150623075724/http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2015-06-23/doc-ifxefurr1048647.shtml|archive-date=2015-06-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

